Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm on Page 02 of Thoracic CT
Then 'CT preliminary examination' checkbox is enabled
And 'MRI preliminary examination' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'CT preliminary examination' checkbox
Then 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'MRI preliminary examination' checkbox
Then 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
